This paper deals with natural language processing and semantic tasks, which are typically covered in the arXiv category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also introduces new concepts and methods that incorporate machine learning and statistical analysis, which are relevant to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
